        <h4>Overview</h4>
        <p class="mb30">TW Media Ltd (“TW Media”, “we,” “us,” and “our”) is committed to securing the private and confidential information of all customers (“you”, “yours”, “client”, and “user”) who visit our website (the “Site”) and make use of our online facilities and services.  The term “Party” may refer to you or TW Media and the term “Parties” refers to both you and TW Media respectfully. Our privacy policy (this “Policy”) has been designed and created to give those affiliated when TW Media the confidence we hold to our commitment and obligation to exceed the required privacy standards.<br>
          <br>
