        <h4>Section 4 - Collection of Information</h4>
        <p class="mb30"> The type of Personal Data (defined below) and Other Data (also defined below and more particularly in Section 7 on Collection and Use of Other Data) we collect depends on how you are specifically interacting with this Site and using our Services. When you visit this Site, make a purchase or attempt to make a purchase, we collect various types of information:<br>
