          b)  Other Business Purposes: This includes data analysis (for example, to improve the efficiency of our Site and Services), editorial and feedback purposes, providing customer support, customising and improving the content and layout of this Site, completing business transactions (for example, to confirm content requested is received by users), development of marketing and promotion plans and materials, statistical analysis of user behaviour (for example, to understand what parts of this Site are of most interest to users), product development, market research, administering individual accounts, and meeting government regulatory requirements such as sales tax collection, audits, etc. Furthermore, we may also use Personal Data of journalist/media contacts for press release distribution or sharing other newsworthy developments related to our business activities. <br>
