        <h4>Section 12 - Data Retention</h4>
        <p class="mb30">You agree to update or correct your Personal Data whenever necessary. TW Media will use and retain your Personal Data for as long as is necessary and only according to its intended purpose for which it was collected, authorised by this Policy, authorised by you, consistent with applicable law and unless and until you ask us to delete this information. The criteria used to determine our retention periods include: <br>
