        <h4>Section 14 - Correct, Update and Conflicts</h4>
        <p class="mb30">If you would like to request to review, correct, update, suppress, delete or otherwise limit our use of your Personal Data that has been previously provided to us, or if you would like to request to receive an electronic copy of your Personal Data for purposes of transmitting it to another company (to the extent this right to data portability is provided to you by applicable law), you may make a request by sending an email to <a href="mailto:help@twmedia.co.uk">help@twmedia.co.uk</a>. We will try to comply with your request as soon as reasonably practicable and consistent with applicable law. <br>
